# protection has "Require review from Code Owners" enabled on main
# (see docs/code_reviews/CLAUDE_PR_REVIEW.md).
/.github/workflows/claude-review-gate.yml   @UncleSaurus
/scripts/verify_claude_review.sh            @UncleSaurus
/scripts/claude_pr_review.sh                @UncleSaurus
/docs/code_reviews/CLAUDE_PR_REVIEW.md      @UncleSaurus
